t theOlympicswhen she retained her 100m and 200m titles in Tokyo, finished last in her season-opening 100m last month, clocking 11.30 secondsat the Prefontaine Classic in Eugene.\", \"from\": 796, \"to\": 1040, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 921, \"end\": 926, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.8867235594160623, \"rank\": 0.12774652244530757, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She last competed in the 200m in April 2023 and appeared to sustain an injury during the 100m at the NYC Grand Prix earlier this month, finishing in 11.48.\", \"from\": 1042, \"to\": 1197, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 31-year-old appointed Reynaldo Walcott, who also workswith compatriot Shelly-Ann Fraser Pryce,as her new coach in November following her split with Shanikie Osbourne.\", \"from\": 1199, \"to\": 1369, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1225, \"end\": 1233, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reynaldo_(footballer,_born_1989)\", \"score\": 0.9561897298989113, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Reynaldo\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reynaldo_(footballer,_born_1989)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reynaldo_(footballer,_born_1989)\"}, {\"begin\": 1234, \"end\": 1241, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Derek_Walcott\", \"score\": 0.9998694033544487, \"rank\": 0.00013054653266816193, \"text\": \"Walcott\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Derek_Walcott\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Derek_Walcott\"}, {\"begin\": 1273, \"end\": 1290, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shelly-Ann_Fraser-Pryce\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shelly-Ann Fra